   In fogpanel each cloud infra resource like cpu,ram etc .. is a billable items. 
Each billable item is treated as services for account user. This billing section 
contain account users used billable items bills on monthly basics. In billing 
we told bills as invoices also this section contain Account user payments for that 
bills. In fogpanel billing we have provide provision for admin to add billable
items for a user or set of users by them self. This section contain those admin 
add items list too.   

